@NODE N5 "History & Todo"
@{fg fill}
KarmaHelp history.
@{fg text}
1.0   @{fg shine} Initial release@{fg text}
1.1   @{fg shine} Added version string :)
      @{fg shine} Made the sorting case-independant.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Rune Jacobsen.
      @{fg shine} KarmaHelp now deletes the guide it creates when you quit it.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Eirik Synnes.
      @{fg shine} Fixed the CX interface infotext.@{fg text}
1.2   @{fg shine} Added recursive scanning when the RECURSIVESCAN tooltype is
       active. Subdirectories will then receive their own button
       with a link to a page containing the directory of that
       subdirectory. An unlimited number of subdirectories
       and sub-subdirectories etc. is supported.
      @{fg text} - This was requested by a lot of people.
      @{fg shine} Added the tooltypes CX_POPUP, which makes KarmaHelp build and
       display the Master Guide each time it is run, and
       AUTOQUIT which makes KarmaHelp quit after having displayed the
       Master Guide.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Joe Yurick.
1.3   @{fg shine} Implemented INCLUDEFILES tooltype. Using standard AmigaDos
       wildcards, you can now select which files are to be displayed
       in the Master Guide. Defaults to excluding .info and .bak files.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Eirik Synnes.
1.4   @{fg shine} Implemented SCANONCE tooltype. If =Yes, the Master Guide will
       only be created if it doesn't allready exist.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Agust Arni Jonsson.
      @{fg shine} Implemented DIRTREE tooltype.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Christopher Dyken.
1.5   @{fg shine} Removed some useless CX code.
      @{fg shine} Added HOTKEYS tooltype.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Colin Thompson.
1.6   @{fg shine} SCANONCE is now aware that KH can scan more than one directory,
       and if the last one scanned is not identical with the one
       requested, it will scan it and create a new Master Guide
      @{fg shine} Optimized the guidecreation a bit.
      @{fg shine} Added the FILTERS tooltype.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Agust Arni Jonsson.
      @{fg shine} Added notification to the directory last scanned.
      @{fg text} - Requested by Finn Kettner.
1.7   @{fg shine} An unlimited number of FILTERS tooltypes are now supported.
       The formatting is still the same. 
      @{fg text} - Requested by Colin Thompson
      @{fg shine} An unlimited number of HOTKEYS tooltypes are now supported.
      @{fg shine} Now supports an unlimited number of main helpdirs. 
      @{fg text} - Requested by Torfinn Ingolfsen, Agust Arni Jonsson, Finn Kettner
         and Michael E. Shea
      @{fg shine} Added TITLESCAN and TITLES tooltypes. 
       Made KarmaHelp compatible with XPKGuide. Set the XPKGUIDE tooltype to =Yes
       if you use XPKGuide as your guideviewer.
       Removed hits when KarmaHelp was run several times. You can now have
       as many KarmaHelps as you want running.
       Enabled the INDEX button on the toolbar. Pressing it will now jump to
       the directory you requested scanned.
2.0    Bumped the revision number :)
@{fg fill}
Todo on KarmaHelp.

